<RulesElement name="Primordial Adept Level 10 Feature" type="Class Feature" internal-id="ID_FMP_CLASS_FEATURE_4306" source="Heroes of the Elemental Chaos" revision-date="11/9/2012 11:46:28 AM" >
    <Category> 10 </Category>
    <Flavor> Your elemental patron places a portion of its essence at your command, drastically enhancing the effectiveness of your attacks then they align with its sphere of influence. </Flavor>
    <specific name="Short Description"> Deal +2 damage rolls with thunder powers and cold, fire, or lightning powers based on your patron </specific>
    <specific name="Level"> 10 </specific>
