           <statadd name="cold:damage" value="+2" type="power" requires="ID_FMP_POWER_16093"/>
	   <statadd name="fire:damage" value="+2" type="power" requires="ID_FMP_POWER_16094"/>
           <statadd name="lightning:damage" value="+2" type="power" requires="ID_FMP_POWER_HF_CW"/>
           <statadd name="thunder:damage" value="+2" type="power"/>
    </rules>
If you chose Solkara's wave, you gain a +2 power bonus to damage rolls with cold powers and thunder powers. If you chose Vezzuvu's eruption, you gain a +2 power bonus to damage rolls with fire powers and thunder powers. If you chose Castanamir's Wrath, you gain a +2 power bonus to lightning powers and thunder powers.
</RulesElement>

